# Project Overview

## Co to za repo

`roduq-design-generator-studio` = **AI-driven design generator** dla Roduq agency.

Fork [nexu-io/open-design](https://github.com/nexu-io/open-design) (Apache-2.0, Next.js 16 + SQLite + Anthropic skills) z Roduq customizations.

## End-state

User wpisuje brief → AI generuje 3 design variants równolegle → user wybiera + eksportuje → `@roduq/cli` (w sister repo `roduq-web-starter`) konsumuje i scaffolduje working website.

**Czas**: brief → AI-designed website w **<5 min** (vs. 2-5 dni manual setup).

## Stack

- **Next.js 16** (upstream — UI w przeglądarce)
- **SQLite** (upstream — local-first state)
- **Anthropic skills** convention (SKILL.md format)
- **MCP server** stdio dla Claude Code bridge
- **TypeScript strict** + exactOptionalPropertyTypes
- **LLM providers**: Anthropic Claude Sonnet 4.6+ (primary) / OpenAI GPT-5 / Google Gemini 2.5 Pro

## Sister repo

[`roduq-web-starter`](../roduq-web-starter/) — main monorepo z Astro 6 + Payload CMS + 29 business modules.

**NIE łączymy kodem** — kontrakt to **file protocol** `~/.roduq/output/{client-id}/` (JSON Schema v1 validated). Patrz `.cursor/rules/004-file-protocol.mdc`.

## Phase plan (7 fazy)

| # | Goal | Scope |
|---|------|-------|
| 1 | Fork + setup | Rebrand, license, .env |
| 2 | 7 Roduq skills | saas-landing / agency / restaurant / clinic / real-estate / product-launch / portfolio |
| 3 | 7 DESIGN.md presets | default / monolith-meadow / tech-modern / warm-editorial / brutalist / soft-pastel / dark-cinematic |
| 4 | Multi-variant skill | 3 designs parallel (Conservative / Modern / Bold) |
| 5 | File export protocol | JSON Schema v1 ajv validation |
| 6 | MCP server bridge | stdio + 3 tools |
| 7 | Testing + polish | Unit + integration + visual regression |

Pełen plan: `.docs/IMPLEMENTATION.md`.

## Non-negotiable rules (TL;DR)

- ❌ NIE łącz w monorepo z roduq-web-starter
- ❌ NIE custom skill format (Anthropic SKILL.md mandatory)
- ❌ NIE proprietary LLM-only features (multi-provider abstraction wymagana)
- ❌ NIE skip schema validation
- ✅ TypeScript strict + Polish-first content
- ✅ License preservation (Apache-2.0 dla upstream forked, proprietary dla Roduq additions)

